title: Multitarget Views.Desktop.Common 3
body: This PR is similar to #1067, which is for a branch with the two commits that fails the automated build.  To gain more information, I am creating this PR to see if just the first of those commits passes the automated build.  This PR is not meant to be completed.  I think it would be better if we could figure out how to get the other branch to pass the automated build and then complete that PR instead.
